  <data name="EmailVerification" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Dear {{ Recipient.DisplayName }}

You have just registered on the Tuckshop online platform.
To complete your registration, please verify your email by clicking  &lt;a href="{{ VerificationUrl }}"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.
NOTE: This link will expire in {{ LinkExpiryHours }} hours

Kind Regards,
Tuckshop</value>
